    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The dual-VANOS system has been overhauled with Beisan components for optimal variable valve timing, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to mitigate floor pan fatigue. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a GKN variable M differential lock. The suspension maintains factory-spec kinematics with refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, ensuring precise turn-in and high-speed stability. This is a mechanically sound example ready for spirited driving.",
      "price": 33800.0,
